BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 180.72 740 Td (Topic 3: Safe Online Shopping) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Only shop on websites that show a padlock icon in the browser address bar.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Look for 'https://' at the beginning of the web address \(the 's' means secure\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Stick to well-known retailers like Amazon, Walmart, and Target online.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Read customer reviews before buying from unfamiliar sellers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Use a credit card instead of debit card for better fraud protection.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Never save your credit card information on websites you rarely use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- Be wary of deals that seem too good to be true - they usually are.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Check the return policy before purchasing anything.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Keep records of all online purchases and confirmation emails.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- Monitor your bank statements weekly for unauthorized charges.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
