BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 180.72 740 Td (Topic 4: Social Media Privacy) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Set your profile to 'Friends Only' so strangers cannot see your posts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Never post your home address, phone number, or daily schedule.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Be careful about posting vacation photos while you are away from home.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Do not accept friend requests from people you do not know in real life.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Review your privacy settings at least every few months.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Be cautious about quizzes that ask personal questions \(maiden name, first pet\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- Never share photos of financial documents, IDs, or boarding passes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Remember that anything you post online can be seen by anyone eventually.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Turn off location sharing on posts so people cannot track where you are.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- If someone you know is acting strange online, call them - their account may be hacked.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
