q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Check the web address carefully - scammers use similar-looking URLs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Look for misspellings in the website name \(amaz0n.com instead of amazon.com\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Legitimate websites have professional design without broken images.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Check if the website has a physical address and phone number listed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Search the company name plus 'scam' or 'reviews' to check reputation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Be suspicious of websites that only accept wire transfers or gift cards.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- Look for a privacy policy and terms of service at the bottom of the page.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- If a website pops up saying your computer is infected, close it immediately.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Bookmark your important websites so you always go to the real one.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- When in doubt, type the web address yourself rather than clicking a link.) Tj ET

endstream
