BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 133.20000000000002 740 Td (Topic 7: Protecting Personal Information) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Never share your Social Security number online or by email.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Be cautious about what personal details you post on social media.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Shred physical mail that contains personal or financial information.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Do not give personal information to callers who contact you first.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Legitimate organizations already have your info - they will not ask for it again.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Be careful filling out online forms - only provide required information.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- Check your credit report annually for accounts you did not open.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Use a separate email address for signing up for newsletters and promotions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Be wary of free WiFi that asks for personal details to connect.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- Review which apps on your phone have access to your contacts and photos.) Tj ET

