BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 185.04000000000002 740 Td (Topic 8: Public WiFi Dangers) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Public WiFi in cafes, airports, and hotels is not secure.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Hackers can see what you do on public WiFi if it is not encrypted.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Never access your bank account or make purchases on public WiFi.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Turn off automatic WiFi connection on your phone in public places.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- If you must use public WiFi, use a VPN \(Virtual Private Network\) for protection.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Verify the network name with staff - hackers create fake hotspots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- A fake hotspot might be named 'Free_Airport_WiFi' to trick you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Use your phone's mobile data instead of public WiFi for sensitive tasks.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Forget public networks after using them so your phone does not reconnect.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- At home, make sure your own WiFi has a strong password to prevent unauthorized access.) Tj ET

