BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 163.44 740 Td (Topic 10: Keeping Devices Updated) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Software updates fix security holes that hackers can exploit.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Turn on automatic updates for your phone, tablet, and computer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- On iPhone: Settings > General > Software Update > Automatic Updates.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- On Android: Settings > System > System Update.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- On Windows: Settings > Update & Security > Windows Update.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Update your web browser regularly - it is your gateway to the internet.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- Update apps from the App Store or Play Store at least weekly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Restart your devices after updates to complete the installation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Old devices that no longer receive updates should be replaced.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- Updates may add new features too, not just security fixes.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
