BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Make sure your background does not show personal information or valuables.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Use meeting passwords when hosting video calls on Zoom or similar.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Do not share meeting links on social media - use direct invitations.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Mute your microphone when not speaking to prevent accidental sharing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Be aware that others can take screenshots during video calls.) Tj ET
