BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Cover your camera with tape or a cover when not using video calls.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- If an unknown person joins your call, remove them immediately.) Tj ET
