BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 193.68 740 Td (Topic 12: Avoiding Malware) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Malware is harmful software that can damage your device or steal data.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Never download software from pop-up ads or unknown websites.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Only download apps from official app stores \(Apple App Store, Google Play\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Do not open email attachments from unknown senders.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Install antivirus software and keep it updated on your computer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Be cautious of free software that seems too good to be true.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- If your device suddenly runs slowly, it might have malware.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Pop-ups saying 'Your computer is infected, call this number' are themselves scams.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Regularly back up your important files to an external drive or cloud.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- If you think you have malware, disconnect from the internet and run a scan.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
