BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Look for the padlock icon and 'https://' before entering financial details.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Set up account alerts for any transaction over a small amount like $25.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Check your bank and credit card statements at least weekly.) Tj ET
