BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Be suspicious of emails claiming to be from your bank asking you to log in.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Bookmark your bank's website and always use that bookmark to visit.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- Consider freezing your credit if you do not plan to apply for new loans.) Tj ET

