BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 172.08 740 Td (Topic 14: Recognizing Deepfakes) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Deepfakes are fake videos or audio made with AI to look real.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- They can make it look like someone said something they never did.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Be skeptical of shocking videos shared on social media.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Look for unnatural facial movements or lip syncing that seems off.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Check if the content appears on legitimate news sources.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Scammers may use AI voice cloning to impersonate family members.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- If a family member calls asking for money, verify by calling them back.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Establish a family code word that only real members would know.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Video quality that looks slightly blurry or waxy may be a deepfake.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- When in doubt, verify information through multiple trusted sources.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
