q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Only download apps from Apple App Store or Google Play Store.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Read the app description and check the developer's name carefully.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Look at the star rating and read recent reviews from other users.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Check what permissions the app requests - a flashlight does not need your contacts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Be suspicious of apps with very few downloads or reviews.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Avoid apps that promise free versions of things that normally cost money.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- Delete apps you no longer use - they can still access your data.) Tj ET
