q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Do not open attachments from people you do not know.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Be suspicious of emails with generic greetings like 'Dear Customer'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Legitimate companies will address you by your actual name.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Never click 'unsubscribe' in spam emails - it confirms your address is active.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Check the sender's full email address, not just the display name.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Be wary of emails creating urgency: 'Your account expires in 24 hours!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- When in doubt, go directly to the company's website instead of clicking links.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Mark spam emails as spam so your email learns to filter them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Use separate email addresses for personal and promotional sign-ups.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- Enable your email's spam filter and check spam folder occasionally for real mail.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
