q 0 G 1 w 80 720 m 532 720 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 690 Td (- Talk to grandchildren about never sharing personal info with strangers online.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Help parents set up parental controls on devices grandchildren use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Know which apps and games grandchildren are using.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Be a safe person they can come to if something online makes them uncomfortable.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Do not post photos of grandchildren with identifying information.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Avoid posting their school name, team, or regular schedule.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 510 Td (- Teach them that not everyone online is who they say they are.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 480 Td (- Encourage open conversations about their online experiences.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Learn about the platforms they use so you can guide them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- Set a good example by practicing safe internet habits yourself.) Tj ET

