BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 660 Td (- Report email scams by forwarding to spam@uce.gov.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 630 Td (- Report phone scams to the FTC and your phone carrier.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 600 Td (- Contact your local police for scams involving financial loss.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 570 Td (- Report identity theft at identitytheft.gov for a recovery plan.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 540 Td (- Notify your bank immediately if financial accounts are compromised.) Tj ET
