BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 450 Td (- Warn friends and family about scams you encounter.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 70 420 Td (- Do not feel embarrassed - scammers are professionals who trick millions of people.) Tj ET

